text: Anastasia Nikolaevna Klimova (, ; born 19 September 1994) is a footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Russian club Yenisey. Born in Ukraine, she represents the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Klimova capped for Armenia at senior level in two friendlies against Lithuania on 4 and 6 March 2020. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Ukrainian women's footballers Category:Sportspeople from Odessa Category:WFC Lehenda-ShVSM Chernihiv players Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Ukrainian expatriate women's footballers Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in Georgia (country) Category:Expatriate footballers in Georgia (country) Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in Belarus Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Belarus Category:Ukrainian emigrants to Armenia Category:Naturalized citizens of Armenia Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers Category:FC Martve players
